data.title: Book Review Sites-Alia
data.meta_description: Book Review Sites-Alia (Autosaved) (Autosaved) - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of over 100 book review blogs and websites with their URLs. The sites cover a wide range of genres including science fiction, fantasy, romance, mystery and more. Many of the blogs are run by individual reviewers who read and provide reviews of books they have read. Others are group sites that feature reviews from multiple reviewers. The list aims to provide resources for readers looking for reviews and discussions of books across many genres and interests.
